{"tid":229193,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求好食粉麵推介","createTime":"2017-05-04T12:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T14:04:33.000Z","uid":14459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3fbadb148115167c3673ad9cea7acde80522d53a","tid":229193,"uid":14459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:23:41.000Z","msg":"其實開呢個post係想哀悼下一間我幾鍾意食嘅魚蛋粉執剩一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n阿媽係潮州人，自細就好鍾意食親戚係大陸攞落嚟嘅魚蛋牛丸墨魚丸，有時冇得食就會去旺角蒂蒂香食下過下引<br />\n<br />\n今日聽到阿媽講旺角嗰間已經執咗真係sad sad地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實去佢度除咗丸最緊要係食墨魚卵餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阿婆過咗身之後身邊已經冇人識整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n頭先search完原來得翻一間係灣仔，但唔就腳已經少好多機會去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以大家仲有冇好食潮州粉麵推介？如果有巴打識窿路不妨話埋俾我聽邊度有墨魚卵餅食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸 非打手，邊有打手等間鋪執淨一間先宜傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815d85a78af3fea5ca307fdf168e3c3efcc9051c","tid":229193,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:25:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2ded977ea4c71918d94e23f4450402615b80c11","tid":229193,"uid":14459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:59:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港仔魚蛋粉</blockquote><br />\n呢間食完口渴喎"},{"pid":"ab53011e5d0c04da651b33b98a4d15154801c64e","tid":229193,"uid":12361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:07:39.000Z","msg":"俾你講完好想去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n旺角廣東道有間25蚊（我覺得好抵嘅）其實唔錯，個師傅仲好有性格<br />\n仲有食過最好食嘅喺澳門紅街市附近間爽爽，墨丸味好出！最中意食紫菜墨丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121b3cc06b35e522e2c38706e6d4a998ba057c4c","tid":229193,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:23:55.000Z","msg":"麵撚留名"},{"pid":"56991b42410ad2af199a4a487560f9e271f63b7b","tid":229193,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:24:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93e9b1649d61031f12a8516248903833a0596a20","tid":229193,"uid":12361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:27:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>俾你講完好想去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n旺角廣東道有間25蚊（我覺得好抵嘅）其實唔錯，個師傅仲好有性格<br />\n仲有食過最好食嘅喺澳門紅街市附近間爽爽，墨丸味好出！最中意食紫菜墨丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n旺角街市果間?</blockquote><br />\n果間近碧街 好細個角落黎<br />\n價錢真係好抵屌<br />\n師傅仲好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利伸：打手"},{"pid":"95d67471f72ddfa8928fedde1c80b8d1cb75fc5b","tid":229193,"uid":14459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:52:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>俾你講完好想去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n旺角廣東道有間25蚊（我覺得好抵嘅）其實唔錯，個師傅仲好有性格<br />\n仲有食過最好食嘅喺澳門紅街市附近間爽爽，墨丸味好出！最中意食紫菜墨丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n旺角街市果間?</blockquote><br />\n果間近碧街 好細個角落黎<br />\n價錢真係好抵屌<br />\n師傅仲好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利伸：打手</blockquote><br />\n我講嗰間叫蒂蒂香<br />\n巴打有興趣可以search下灣仔嗰間地址試下，我就未去過嗰間，但應該唔差得遠<br />\n另外你講嗰間可唔可以俾名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去開試下"},{"pid":"64fee2580de23f73ad8bedc581c736508d5a66c2","tid":229193,"uid":14459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:52:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>麵撚留名</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf37cc1c71718a8545a56a78